<plot>Growing weary of his girl friend, Kentaro moves to a new apartment. One day in summer, he sees his ugly neighbor come out from the room together with many beautiful women around. It bothers him big time and eventually he reaches to an answer to this mystery: the very existence of a certain can named "BIJO-CAN". Kentaro, getting hold of this BIJOCAN, finally succeeds to produce his own ideally beautiful woman, Bijo.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?070284</url></doc>
